title: Lido Beach and Burger
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant and bar at the beach of Murnau at Staffelsee. It's linked with the local and protected swimming area. Menu has a couple vegan burgers as well as a few vegan suitable sides. Beverages include coconut water and ChariTea (faire trade tea), has soymilk.
